com.amazonaws.kinesisvideo.producer

Interface ServiceCallbacks

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultServiceCallbacksImpl

    public interface ServiceCallbacks
    Interface to the KinesisVideo Producer Stream Service Callbacks functionality. These will be used for scheduling and managing the service calls.
